## Notice

This Helm chart is designed to deploy and manage the Worker-Sync application
in Kubernetes environments. It includes configurations for:

- Database synchronization and auditing
- Real-time change data capture (CDC)
- Message queue integration
- Monitoring and alerting
- Security and compliance features
- High availability and scaling

Users are responsible for ensuring compliance with all applicable licenses
when using this chart in their environments.

